text: Åsa Tindra Jinder Otter, born 9 October 1963 in Danderyd, Sweden, is a Swedish nyckelharpa player, composer, producer, songwriter, author and lecturer. She has scored chart successes at the Swedish album chart. == References == ==Other websites== *Åsa Jinder's website Category:Swedish musicians Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish writers
